channel.title: GDX Online (Prv Server)
channel.description:
[center][size=5]GDX Online[/size] [size=1]A KalOnline Private Server
[/size][hr][size=2][u]About:[/u]
[/size][size=2]This is a 3D MMORPG, let me tell you: It is amazing! I would not just make a thread about any old game.
With so many features such as: quests, transformation, multi-attack modes, various armor, three job types: Knight, Magician, and Ranger, and many more.
[/size][hr][size=2][u]Server Time
[/u]Click here: [url=http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/city.html?n=179]http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/city.html?n=179[/url] The time when this game is on is: about 4PM to 12PM (based on the time in the link above).[/size][hr][size=2][u]Screen shots & Videos [/u] YouTube Video: [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wQcVpMohPdw]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wQcVpMohPdw[/url] - I'm making a trailer for the game, as asked by the Admin.
Most of the screen shots are here: [url=http://gdxonline.no-ip.info/GDXOnline/gallery.php]http://gdxonline.no-ip.info/GDXOnline/gallery.php[/url]
But since it's a free upload site, it has other stuff in it, but if you scroll down, you can see the game shots.
One of the screen shots: [url=http://gdxonline.no-ip.info/GDXOnline/upload/shot_2008_3_29_016.jpg]http://gdxonline.no-ip.info/GDXOnline/upload/shot_2008_3_29_016.jpg[/url] [/size][hr][size=2][u]Personnel Opinion[/u]
I think this game is wonderful. Compressed, it comes up to ~270MB. It's amazing. It's similar to WoW, and I could proudly say this game is a must play. It's addicted once you've played it. Just try it! [/size][hr][size=2][u]Download [/u] The link to the client download can be found here : [url=http://www.sendspace.com/file/rr1my4]http://www.sendspace.com/file/rr1my4[/url][/size]
-Keep the spam and flame low ;)[/center]
